name: Foodtastic
overview: Three teams of food artists transform iconic characters into extravagant masterpieces that tell a story from Disney's legendary IP. The food sculptures will be judged on their design, technical skills and narrative, and not by taste. Unused food from each competition will be donated to local food banks.
tagline: Never stop playing with your food.
